1
00:01:31,740 --> 00:01:41,220
=The Glory=

2
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:44,040
(Seclusion)
Miss Hanyan, please do not approach.

3
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,510
Otherwise, you will be killed.

4
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:47,350
Why?

5
00:01:47,790 --> 00:01:48,890
His Majesty has ordered me

6
00:01:49,230 --> 00:01:50,790
to protect Mr. Zhuang.

7
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:52,590
Anyone who wants to hurt him

8
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:54,590
will be executed on the spot
before reporting.

9
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:55,950
I can die,

10
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:59,120
but before that, he must pay the price.

11
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:00,160
Stop her.

12
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:35,990
Stop.

13
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,680
Fu Yunxi, move aside!

14
00:02:43,740 --> 00:02:45,860
With His Majesty's orders,
I can't let you through.

15
00:02:52,310 --> 00:02:53,750
Either kill me,

16
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:55,590
or I will never let him go.

17
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:56,630
Zhuang Hanyan,

18
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,590
this is not revenge;

19
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,520
it's throwing your life away.

20
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,280
Lock her in Yuzhu Manor.

21
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,520
Yes.

22
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:51,840
I know

23
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,280
what Zhuang Shiyang has done.

24
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,840
She has multiple knife wounds
on her body.

25
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:01,800
Each wound

26
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,590
is evidence of Zhuang Shiyang's crime.

27
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:12,190
I will not let him go unpunished.

28
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,480
The Hanlin Academy's archives
were set on fire,

29
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,020
and the Comprehensive Encyclopedia
was destroyed.

30
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:26,950
Now, only Zhuang Shiyang

31
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:28,600
can rewrite and redraw it.

32
00:04:29,310 --> 00:04:30,800
This is of national importance.

33
00:04:31,190 --> 00:04:33,240
His life is now worth more than gold.

34
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,750
I am under orders to protect him.

35
00:04:36,630 --> 00:04:38,120
If he dies at your hands,

36
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,680
I will also be held responsible.

37
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,880
Fu Yunxi,

38
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,230
what does your life

39
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:47,800
have to do with me?

40
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,800
You can't get close to him.

41
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,830
I will not allow you to approach him.

42
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,160
But you can.

43
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,430
This is not a discussion,

44
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,480
nor a request.

45
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:02,920
This is a threat.

46
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,260
You fear the crime
of dereliction of duty.

47
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:09,150
Don't you fear the exposure
of your identity as Pei's adopted son?

48
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,830
I have something on you.

49
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:15,120
I can also kill you.

50
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:18,480
I can even make your entire family

51
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,270
die with you.

52
00:05:27,510 --> 00:05:28,560
Are you crazy?

53
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,000
You're not the victim.

54
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,480
Of course, you can say I'm crazy.

55
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,320
Zhuang Hanyan.

56
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,800
I know asking you to calm down now

57
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:43,750
might be too harsh,

58
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,360
but think carefully.

59
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,310
What is Zhuang Shiyang

60
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,630
most afraid of right now?

61
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,120
He's most afraid
of you and me joining forces.

62
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,560
He knows that after killing Ruan Xiwen,

63
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,950
you and I will unite against him,

64
00:05:59,430 --> 00:06:01,240
so he went to great lengths
to set this trap.

65
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:03,360
On one hand, he can protect himself,

66
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,600
and on the other,
he can sow discord between us,

67
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:08,070
forcing his two biggest enemies
to kill each other,

68
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,680
so he can sit back, watch the fight,

69
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,160
and profit from it.

70
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,630
If you remain blind to this,

71
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,390
you will fall into his trap.

72
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,750
You've always been clever.

73
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:21,190
Don't lose your sense of reason
because of your anger,

74
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,830
or in the end,

75
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,260
you'll lose everything.

76
00:06:28,430 --> 00:06:30,310
My weakness has been exposed to you,

77
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,270
and that is my family.

78
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,560
You want revenge for your mother,

79
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,950
but I also have people
I want to protect.

80
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:38,830
So now,

81
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,560
I can't help you kill Zhuang Shiyang,

82
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:43,800
but everything

83
00:06:45,230 --> 00:06:46,390
can be planned slowly.

84
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,120
We can act when the time is right.

85
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,240
Fu Yunxi,

86
00:07:11,070 --> 00:07:12,680
I want to ask you one more thing.

87
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:14,670
What?

88
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:16,750
What is your connection

89
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,480
with the Pei faction?

90
00:07:33,540 --> 00:07:37,540
=Episode 19=

91
00:07:38,580 --> 00:07:42,300
(Six years ago)

92
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,270
I am willing.

93
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:46,070
There may be no reward for this,

94
00:07:46,770 --> 00:07:47,930
but if something goes wrong,

95
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,580
(Wen Mingchang, Chief Minister)
only you

96
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:51,630
will be blamed,
and there will be no way back.

97
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:53,510
Since Pei Dafu has shown favor to me,

98
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,310
if I refuse,

99
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:56,920
it might bring trouble.

100
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:59,120
It's better to pretend to submit.

101
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:02,750
Besides, his gang deceives His Majesty
and disrupts the government.

102
00:08:02,870 --> 00:08:05,010
The common people have suffered
from it for too long.

103
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:07,920
I'm willing to contribute
to eliminating the corrupt.

104
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:10,370
There are many spies
from the Pei faction in the court.

105
00:08:10,390 --> 00:08:11,830
Only you and I can know

106
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,560
you've become a spy.

107
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:16,160
It must not be revealed to anyone else.

108
00:08:16,310 --> 00:08:17,430
I understand.

109
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,000
Six years ago,

110
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:22,790
Pei Dafu, the Seal-holding Director
of the Zuohang Gang,

111
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:24,360
intended to recruit me.

112
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,870
(Brightness, Pei Mansion)

113
00:08:26,870 --> 00:08:29,190
Chief Minister Wen secretly
summoned me late at night

114
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:31,000
and told me to feign submission

115
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,440
and gain Pei Dafu's trust.

116
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:33,460
(Brightness, Pei Mansion)

117
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,790
Then, I'd find a chance

118
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:37,080
to eliminate the Zuohang Gang.

119
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:52,240
Mr. Fu, I'd long heard
of your remarkable skills.

120
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:54,120
Tonight, I can see

121
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,870
you've lived up to your reputation.

122
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:59,790
Greetings, Mr. Pei.

123
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,840
Earlier, I acted recklessly

124
00:10:02,270 --> 00:10:03,630
and injured your guards.

125
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,200
Please punish me.

126
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,670
Lives

127
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,840
don't matter.

128
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,870
What matters

129
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,910
is talent.

130
00:10:13,510 --> 00:10:14,910
Mr. Fu,

131
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:17,440
would you be willing

132
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:20,240
to impeach me in court?

133
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,840
Before I can serve you,

134
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:23,750
I shall appear as your enemy.

135
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,150
I obey.

136
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,440
Talking to a smart person

137
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:32,960
is indeed the most effortless.

138
00:10:33,550 --> 00:10:36,600
For those who are loyal

139
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:39,240
and devoted to the Zuohang Gang,

140
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:44,150
I will not treat them unfairly.

141
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,080
Thank you, My Lord.

142
00:10:46,630 --> 00:10:47,600
Since that night,

143
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:50,150
I'd spent a lot of effort and energy

144
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,240
to gain Pei Dafu's trust

145
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,180
and favor step by step.

146
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,750
He accepted me as his adopted son,

147
00:10:55,510 --> 00:10:57,930
and I tried to gather evidence
against the Pei faction.

148
00:10:58,510 --> 00:11:00,470
(Pei Mansion)
But just as I was about to succeed,

149
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:01,580
(Wen Mingchang's Coffin)

150
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:03,630
Pei Dafu discovered
Mr. Wen's plan to eliminate

151
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:06,580
(Spirit Tablet of Late Husband, Wen)
the Pei faction,

152
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:08,510
and Mr. Wen then died.

153
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:09,840
No one could prove

154
00:11:10,270 --> 00:11:11,840
my identity anymore.

155
00:11:12,850 --> 00:11:15,200
(Spirit Tablet of Late Husband, Wen)
I was deeply involved.

156
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,790
I was aware of the danger I was in.

157
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,320
If the Zuohang Gang were to fall,

158
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:21,010
I wouldn't just lose my own life,

159
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,030
but my entire family
would be implicated.

160
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,320
To protect myself,

161
00:11:25,770 --> 00:11:27,120
I decided to compile the evidence

162
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,430
against the Pei faction
and their spies within the court

163
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:30,890
I had collected over the years

164
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:32,200
into a secret letter

165
00:11:32,870 --> 00:11:34,150
to send to the Palace asap.

166
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:35,590
This move

167
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:37,150
would not only bring down Pei Dafu

168
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:39,320
but prove my innocence to His Majesty.

169
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,390
However, at this moment...

170
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,440
My Lord,

171
00:11:48,610 --> 00:11:50,110
the Capital is about to face a storm.

172
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:52,120
Director Pei worked
with imperial concubines

173
00:11:52,140 --> 00:11:53,950
to manipulate the choice
of the Crown Prince.

174
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:54,980
This enraged His Majesty.

175
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,240
His Majesty has issued an edict

176
00:11:56,300 --> 00:11:57,740
to throw him into the imperial prison

177
00:11:57,760 --> 00:12:00,310
and have the Judicial Review
clear the Pei faction remnants.

178
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,390
My last escape route was blocked.

179
00:12:03,030 --> 00:12:05,510
I had no choice but to take a risk.

180
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:07,380
(Court of Judicial Review)

181
00:12:07,790 --> 00:12:10,200
You want to investigate the Pei faction?

182
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,280
Yes.

183
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:13,340
(Justice Without Mercy)
This involves great stakes,

184
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:15,000
and it is an excellent chance

185
00:12:15,270 --> 00:12:17,080
to earn merit before His Majesty.

186
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:20,840
Why should I entrust you with it?

187
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,910
The remnants are hidden
everywhere in the court.

188
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:25,270
There are certainly
their spies among us.

189
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,080
Mr. Yan,

190
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,200
who can you trust except for me?

191
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:31,310
I've been at odds
with the Zuohang Gang for years.

192
00:12:31,310 --> 00:12:33,420
(Clean and Incorruptible)
You should've heard of it.

193
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:36,030
It's not fame or profit
that's driving me to handle this case.

194
00:12:36,090 --> 00:12:38,040
For all these years,
I've watched the Pei faction

195
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:40,680
corrupt the court, harm loyal officials,
and oppress the people,

196
00:12:40,730 --> 00:12:43,050
leading to the destruction
of countless innocent families.

197
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:45,390
Now, only by personally
eliminating this gang

198
00:12:45,390 --> 00:12:47,360
can I release the pent-up frustration
in my heart.

199
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,120
I hope you will allow it.

200
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,150
Be cautious.

201
00:12:54,390 --> 00:12:56,750
I will do my best to root out
the Pei fraction remnants

202
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:58,080
and leave no one behind.

203
00:12:58,080 --> 00:13:00,020
(Peace, Song Residence)

204
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:02,600
I made strong efforts
to work on the case

205
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:04,350
of the Zuohang Gang

206
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,750
partly because I understood

207
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:06,790
the Pei faction deeply,

208
00:13:07,090 --> 00:13:09,360
and I could contribute
to the purification of the court

209
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,490
and the peace of the people.

210
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,230
It was also partly because I needed
to protect myself.

211
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,390
Will you confess?

212
00:13:19,630 --> 00:13:20,480
Mr. Fu,

213
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,840
Director Pei's wealth

214
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,670
is not in my hands.

215
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,840
Pei Dafu has been embezzling for years.

216
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:29,760
It's said that his fortune could rival
half of the national treasury.

217
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:31,670
We've raided his house for days,

218
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,200
yet we found no riches in sight.

219
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:35,000
He could even be praised
as a clean official.

220
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,630
Now, among the Pei faction,

221
00:13:36,790 --> 00:13:37,870
you are the only one

222
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:40,000
who has had financial dealings with him.

223
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,750
If you don't admit it,

224
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,480
you'll suffer more.

225
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:44,590
Wait.

226
00:13:44,870 --> 00:13:45,710
I'll tell you.

227
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:47,390
Tell us the truth now.

228
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,600
Pei Dafu's wealth

229
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,200
is in the hands

230
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:53,120
of his adopted son.

231
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:55,750
Adopted son? Explain it.

232
00:13:56,800 --> 00:14:00,200
This man is Pei Dafu's
only trusted confidant.

233
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:03,390
Pei accepted him as his adopted son.

234
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:04,840
For many years,

235
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:07,360
he's been laundering
Pei's ill-gotten money

236
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:08,750
and hiding Pei's wealth.

237
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:10,390
But this man's whereabouts are secret,

238
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,270
and he never reveals himself.

239
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:17,440
I don't know who this man really is.

240
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:20,630
If you're making up lies
to avoid punishment,

241
00:14:20,830 --> 00:14:22,320
you'll receive more severe punishment.

242
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:24,240
With the current situation,

243
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:26,790
all I want is to keep my life.

244
00:14:27,150 --> 00:14:29,630
How would I dare conceal anything?

245
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,840
Have you heard about this?

246
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,910
Sorry for my incompetence.

247
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,750
This is the first time I've heard

248
00:14:35,870 --> 00:14:37,750
that Pei Dafu has an adopted son

249
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,360
who hides the illicit wealth for him.

250
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,630
Report this to His Majesty.

251
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:43,470
Yes.

252
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:46,630
It was only that night I learned

253
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:49,390
that Pei Dafu had

254
00:14:49,750 --> 00:14:51,120
more than one adopted son.

255
00:14:52,100 --> 00:14:53,770
As everyone knew
Pei had an adopted son,

256
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,200
only by capturing this adopted son

257
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:57,120
could I ensure my safety.

258
00:14:58,360 --> 00:15:00,630
But after searching every force
of the Capital,

259
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,120
I could never find a trace

260
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:04,120
of this adopted son.

261
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:07,390
As you already know,

262
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:10,800
I later went to investigate in Yinan
under the pretext of the Danzhou case

263
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:12,670
and obtained the testimony
of the DCC's head.

264
00:15:12,910 --> 00:15:14,120
Only then did I realize

265
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:17,660
that the man I had been searching for
might have been right in front of me,

266
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:18,870
and it was Zhuang Shiyang.

267
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:21,150
Later, with your help,

268
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:23,630
I eavesdropped
on your mother's secret schemes

269
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:26,630
and manipulated the drama
at the Yinan Guild Hall

270
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:29,560
to have Zhuang Shiyang executed
under the name of Pei's adopted son

271
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:32,440
and close this major case.

272
00:15:33,350 --> 00:15:34,750
I had been plotting for a long time,

273
00:15:34,750 --> 00:15:36,080
but the plan failed

274
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:38,030
because Wu Youzhi's body

275
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:40,030
was exposed.

276
00:15:41,630 --> 00:15:43,080
Perhaps I should never have gone

277
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:44,770
to such lengths
to save the Zhuang family.

278
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,710
Though it would've also been a dead end,

279
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:50,490
at least my mother's wishes
would've been fulfilled

280
00:15:51,150 --> 00:15:53,840
by dragging Zhuang Shiyang
to the underworld along with her.

281
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,600
But in recent days,

282
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,720
her legs healed,

283
00:15:58,230 --> 00:16:00,070
and she escaped
the place that she disdained

284
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:03,030
and even enjoyed moments of joy
with her beloved.

285
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,000
Perhaps these have been
the happiest days

286
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,200
of her life in decades.

287
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:09,550
Zhuang Shiyang will never stop here.

288
00:16:10,070 --> 00:16:12,240
This national pest and family scourge

289
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:14,840
must be brought to justice swiftly

290
00:16:15,660 --> 00:16:17,270
to let the deceased rest in peace

291
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:21,720
and to uphold justice.

292
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:23,840
Can't he be accused

293
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:27,200
based on this murder case?

294
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:30,080
This man is always devious and crafty.

295
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,200
Now, we have no witnesses or evidence.

296
00:16:32,870 --> 00:16:34,080
That fire

297
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,720
destroyed everything.

298
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:37,270
Moreover, besides your mother,

299
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,630
we can't even prove

300
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:40,630
who the other three bodies belonged to.

301
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:44,480
It's true that a cowardly rat

302
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:46,480
lives the longest.

303
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,360
This man has already lost his sanity.

304
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:52,520
You can't stay in the Zhuang Residence
any longer.

305
00:16:58,510 --> 00:16:59,350
Fu Yunxi,

306
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,960
does the deal you proposed before

307
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:03,120
still stand?

308
00:17:04,070 --> 00:17:05,240
I will be your wife,

309
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,200
and you will be my strategist.

310
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,310
Within a year,

311
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:12,400
help me become the noblest lady
in the Capital.

312
00:17:13,070 --> 00:17:13,910
Why?

313
00:17:14,070 --> 00:17:16,000
Under the pretext of rewriting
the encyclopedia,

314
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:18,310
Zhuang Shiyang has managed
to protect his life.

315
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,350
If he drags this on for years,

316
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,480
should I just wait idly by?

317
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:26,550
Now he can so easily control us

318
00:17:26,850 --> 00:17:28,680
because he has had support

319
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:30,590
and gained greater power.

320
00:17:31,350 --> 00:17:32,960
I must find support to rely on too.

321
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:34,510
Otherwise,

322
00:17:34,790 --> 00:17:35,830
from now on,

323
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:38,830
it will be harder for me
to protect myself.

324
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:41,640
How could I continue fighting him then?

325
00:17:42,720 --> 00:17:43,590
Zhuang Hanyan,

326
00:17:44,440 --> 00:17:45,880
those who flatter the powerful

327
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:47,750
ultimately do not end well.

328
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:53,350
Do you have another solution?

329
00:17:57,640 --> 00:18:00,110
Now, Zhuang Shiyang
is our common enemy.

330
00:18:00,530 --> 00:18:02,440
If you ally with me and help me,

331
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,920
you will be helping yourself as well.

332
00:18:04,550 --> 00:18:05,390
Moreover,

333
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:07,550
just as you said before,

334
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:10,000
if something happens to you,

335
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:12,920
I will certainly protect your family.

336
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,440
Isn't this exactly what you want?

337
00:18:17,350 --> 00:18:19,230
Besides, for the greater good
of the country,

338
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:22,640
don't you want
to personally capture him?

339
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,200
When do you wish to marry me?

340
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:30,560
Tomorrow.

341
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:33,480
Good, tomorrow it is.

342
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:36,550
Before that,

343
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:40,480
there is one thing
you must take care of.

344
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:42,640
Due to the Yinan Guild Hall incident,

345
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:44,850
I have been removed
from the Zhuang family register

346
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:46,790
and am no longer considered a Zhuang.

347
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,640
The marriage contract you hold

348
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,750
is thus invalid.

349
00:18:51,550 --> 00:18:52,960
So, before I marry you,

350
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:55,310
I must be reinstated
in the family register

351
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:58,750
so Zhuang Shiyang can't meddle again.

352
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:01,030
This is not difficult; I will handle it.

353
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:03,830
But you must also understand
that after we marry,

354
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:05,310
our lives, honor, and disgrace

355
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:07,920
will all be tied to our families.

356
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,720
You must consult with me on everything

357
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,750
and never act rashly.

358
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:14,800
Sure.

359
00:19:16,110 --> 00:19:17,000
I promise you.

360
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,640
(From now on,)

361
00:19:36,790 --> 00:19:39,110
(I will no longer be anyone's pawn.)

362
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,960
(I want to be)

363
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,790
(the one who holds the pieces.)

364
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:47,440
(Mother,)

365
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:50,160
(after I avenge you,)

366
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,960
(and the devil is punished,)

367
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:56,720
(I will return to inscribe words
on your tombstones.)

368
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:03,420
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)

369
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,960
This time,
the Hanlin Academy caught fire.

370
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:07,830
It's all thanks to you
finding a solution.

371
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,680
Once this is settled,

372
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:12,200
you will definitely be promoted.

373
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:14,270
I don't hope for that.

374
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:16,440
I only seek to atone for my mistakes.

375
00:20:21,240 --> 00:20:22,110
Hanyan,

376
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:24,310
let's eat together.

377
00:20:24,640 --> 00:20:26,540
Father, do you still dare
to let me come close?

378
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,350
Don't you fear that I will strike

379
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,000
when you're unguarded?

380
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:32,750
Stop that nonsense.

381
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:34,000
Come here.

382
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,480
Oh, right.

383
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:38,720
I was wrong.

384
00:20:40,070 --> 00:20:41,270
Father, you must be hoping

385
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:43,550
I will act against you

386
00:20:44,790 --> 00:20:46,720
so that you can

387
00:20:46,720 --> 00:20:48,590
get rid of me.

388
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,920
Ruyin, leave us.

389
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:52,840
Yes.

390
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:01,430
Hanyan...

391
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:03,310
I'm already engaged to Fu Yunxi.

392
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,470
What?

393
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:08,590
Tomorrow morning,
he'll come to pick me up.

394
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:11,240
Who arranged this marriage?

395
00:21:11,720 --> 00:21:13,350
If you still want your dignity,

396
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:15,920
you should follow my plan.

397
00:21:16,270 --> 00:21:17,480
You're a young lady.

398
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:19,550
How can you be engaged
to your brother-in-law?

399
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:20,640
How inappropriate.

400
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:21,590
Father,

401
00:21:22,110 --> 00:21:25,110
when did our family
have a sense of shame?

402
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:28,000
When I first entered the residence,

403
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,590
Mother once scolded us bitterly.

404
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:33,350
She said that the Zhuangs

405
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:35,440
might look kind,

406
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:38,030
but we all were cruel beasts

407
00:21:38,350 --> 00:21:39,960
and reapers in hell.

408
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:42,680
At the time, I didn't understand
what she meant.

409
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:45,350
But now, every word seems true.

410
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:48,550
Why is it that you feel ashamed today

411
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:50,720
when it comes to my marriage?

412
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,830
You unfilial daughter,

413
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:55,550
how dare you speak
such rebellious words!

414
00:21:58,510 --> 00:21:59,350
Right.

415
00:22:00,110 --> 00:22:02,680
Our family is a family of virtue.

416
00:22:04,110 --> 00:22:05,830
Tomorrow morning, I will get married.

417
00:22:06,310 --> 00:22:08,480
Father, please prepare my dowry.

418
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:11,110
Rules must be observed
to avoid humiliation.

419
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:14,200
As for the revenge for Mother's death

420
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,590
and the tragedy of her maiden family,

421
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:19,310
we will

422
00:22:20,750 --> 00:22:22,790
settle those accounts in time.

423
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:57,110
Miss Hanyan,

424
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:58,590
did you call for me?

425
00:22:59,830 --> 00:23:00,680
Shuhong,

426
00:23:01,310 --> 00:23:03,160
I'm about to marry Mr. Fu.

427
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:05,030
Before I go,

428
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:06,920
this is your deed.

429
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,110
If you wish to leave,

430
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:10,070
you will be free from now on.

431
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:12,550
Miss Hanyan, are you sending me away?

432
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:14,200
I'm not sending you away.

433
00:23:16,550 --> 00:23:18,070
My mother trusted you,

434
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:20,200
so I must treat you well.

435
00:23:22,550 --> 00:23:23,510
Miss, forgive me.

436
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:25,510
- I...
- Get up.

437
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:30,480
I have never blamed you,

438
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:33,550
or I wouldn't have
clarified everything now.

439
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,310
You knew all along?

440
00:23:37,110 --> 00:23:39,240
Jilan and Shuhong

441
00:23:40,030 --> 00:23:42,680
sound like a pair.

442
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:46,240
Mother placed you by my side

443
00:23:46,830 --> 00:23:49,830
but never thought of changing your name.

444
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,880
It was a big oversight.

445
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:54,030
Besides, when Mother left,

446
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:56,160
she only took you two.

447
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:59,070
She didn't plan
to keep hiding it from me.

448
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,710
I'm too foolish to realize that.

449
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:04,000
But

450
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,820
aren't you going to live with the madam?

451
00:24:06,510 --> 00:24:08,270
Mother and Mr. Yuwen

452
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:10,960
have found a peaceful place

453
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:13,550
and will stay together forever.

454
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,510
Nanny Chen and Jilan

455
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,270
have gone with them.

456
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:23,240
We can't catch up to them now.

457
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:24,790
These past few days,

458
00:24:25,350 --> 00:24:26,680
I've been confused and worried.

459
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:29,070
Have the madam and the others...?

460
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,030
Miss Hanyan,

461
00:24:34,550 --> 00:24:36,480
it's not my place to ask
about my master,

462
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:39,400
but as an orphan, I have no parents.

463
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,350
Had it not been for the madam,

464
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:43,830
I would've long been dead
on the streets.

465
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:46,200
Such kindness can't be forgotten.

466
00:24:46,480 --> 00:24:48,600
Miss Hanyan, if you can take me
as your dowry maid,

467
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:50,830
I'll be loyal to you
for the rest of my life.

468
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:56,400
I want to avenge my mother.

469
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:01,200
This path is dangerous.

470
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:04,790
Are you truly willing to follow me?

471
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:06,480
Yes.

472
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:15,590
(Gongtong Chamber)
I won't live anymore.

473
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,880
None of you will be spared.

474
00:25:18,080 --> 00:25:20,400
I will burn down this house.

475
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:26,200
Hold Miss Yushan down.

476
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,040
Who dares?

477
00:25:27,480 --> 00:25:28,480
Who dares come near me?

478
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:29,720
I will die with you all.

479
00:25:29,960 --> 00:25:31,430
- Hold her down.
- You...

480
00:25:31,550 --> 00:25:32,480
Let go!

481
00:25:33,750 --> 00:25:35,790
I'm going to find Zhuang Hanyan.

482
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:37,590
Keep your voice down.

483
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:39,790
There are heavy guards at the house.

484
00:25:39,790 --> 00:25:41,200
How dare you cause such trouble?

485
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:42,750
Miss Yushan,

486
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,750
Ms. Zhou is doing this
for your own good.

487
00:25:44,750 --> 00:25:46,400
Please stop making trouble.

488
00:25:47,110 --> 00:25:48,880
Go away. What are you doing?

489
00:25:48,960 --> 00:25:49,960
Go away.

490
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:54,240
Mom,

491
00:25:55,200 --> 00:25:57,480
didn't you promise me

492
00:25:58,160 --> 00:26:00,400
that Yunxi would marry me?

493
00:26:02,400 --> 00:26:04,680
Do you think I'm not worthy of him?

494
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:06,830
What's so great about Fu Yunxi?

495
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:08,350
Why are you so bewitched by him?

496
00:26:08,790 --> 00:26:09,630
Mom,

497
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,510
I've long since grown tired of Fu Yunxi,

498
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:15,750
but Yushan truly loves him.

499
00:26:17,110 --> 00:26:18,920
Now, aren't you going to help her?

500
00:26:19,750 --> 00:26:21,000
You two, stop.

501
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:22,680
Do you not realize this?

502
00:26:23,110 --> 00:26:24,550
Zhuang Hanyan left but returned,

503
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:26,400
and then she was
secretly engaged to Fu Yunxi.

504
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:29,510
All these strange things
are bound to bring trouble.

505
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:31,310
If you two continue causing trouble now,

506
00:26:31,310 --> 00:26:33,310
you're treating your lives as nothing.

507
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:35,160
What trouble could there be?

508
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:37,550
Zhuang Hanyan is just fickle.

509
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:38,440
She left the Capital

510
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:40,270
and realized she couldn't bear
to leave Yunxi,

511
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:43,160
so she came back to marry him.

512
00:26:43,350 --> 00:26:45,480
In that case, they'd be
in love with each other.

513
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:46,790
What does it have to do with you?

514
00:26:47,160 --> 00:26:48,000
Yes.

515
00:26:48,510 --> 00:26:50,030
I am shameless,

516
00:26:50,310 --> 00:26:52,240
immoral,

517
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:54,070
and unreasonable.

518
00:26:54,480 --> 00:26:56,550
Even if I can't marry Yunxi,

519
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:59,070
I can't let her succeed.

520
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:02,670
Mom.

521
00:27:03,030 --> 00:27:03,870
Mom,

522
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:05,830
I beg you.

523
00:27:06,310 --> 00:27:07,510
Please help me.

524
00:27:07,510 --> 00:27:09,270
Please help me, okay?

525
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:12,320
Mom,

526
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:14,880
please help Yushan.

527
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:18,350
Yushan,

528
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,440
I also want to help you,

529
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:25,200
but during these turbulent times,

530
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:27,400
we must not act rashly.

531
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:31,350
Don't blame me for being heartless.

532
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:33,680
I am doing this for your own good.

533
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:37,070
Keep an eye on Miss Yushan.

534
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:37,910
Without my order,

535
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:39,480
she can't leave Gongtong Chamber.

536
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:40,720
Yes.

537
00:27:41,590 --> 00:27:42,430
Mom.

538
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,200
Mom...

539
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:47,520
Don't cry.

540
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,000
It's alright.

541
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:57,820
(Kindness Benefits Children)

542
00:28:17,500 --> 00:28:21,140
(Composure)

543
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:23,630
Mr. Zhuang,

544
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,270
where are you going?

545
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:27,720
My family has a joyful event tomorrow.

546
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:30,030
There are many
trivial matters to attend to.

547
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,920
I must go out for a bit.

548
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:34,830
I will return soon.

549
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,720
What are you doing?

550
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:43,480
Mr. Fu has ordered

551
00:28:44,110 --> 00:28:46,440
that if you're leaving home,

552
00:28:46,790 --> 00:28:48,750
we must follow you closely.

553
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:53,270
Very well.

554
00:28:58,420 --> 00:29:01,260
(Sincerity and Noble)

555
00:29:03,680 --> 00:29:05,110
Good, good.

556
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,080
Here.

557
00:29:13,680 --> 00:29:15,680
You've finally agreed to remarry.

558
00:29:15,880 --> 00:29:18,880
I can now rest easy.

559
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:21,270
Hanyan is good-looking,

560
00:29:21,550 --> 00:29:23,240
and she has courage and wisdom.

561
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:25,830
Even Lingzhi is willing to be with her.

562
00:29:26,750 --> 00:29:29,270
You two are indeed a good match.

563
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,210
Mother, thanks for allowing this.

564
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:33,350
But I still think

565
00:29:34,070 --> 00:29:37,200
Hanyan lacks a bit of virtue.

566
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:39,880
Perhaps you should reconsider.

567
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,480
If we keep considering,

568
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,750
he may end up single his whole life.

569
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:52,760
My Lord...

570
00:29:56,070 --> 00:29:57,000
Go to work then.

571
00:30:03,230 --> 00:30:04,100
What's the matter?

572
00:30:04,110 --> 00:30:05,160
Zhuang Shiyang just left

573
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,510
to meet a matchmaker at a tavern.

574
00:30:06,580 --> 00:30:07,980
I went to investigate and found out

575
00:30:08,000 --> 00:30:09,890
the matchmaker is notoriously mercenary,

576
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:12,580
specializing in the concubine business
that blesses the husband.

577
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:14,780
Zhuang Shiyang might marry
his daughter off tonight.

578
00:30:14,790 --> 00:30:16,720
My Lord, you must decide quickly.

579
00:30:17,200 --> 00:30:18,880
According to Zhuang Shiyang's plan,

580
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:21,070
he won't allow Zhuang Hanyan

581
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:23,000
to escape his control so easily.

582
00:30:23,550 --> 00:30:25,030
I'm afraid the marriage is just a ruse

583
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:27,480
to send his daughter away

584
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:28,680
to avoid suspicion

585
00:30:29,110 --> 00:30:31,270
and then kill her on the way.

586
00:30:31,860 --> 00:30:32,710
Then...

587
00:30:32,830 --> 00:30:33,790
My wedding

588
00:30:34,110 --> 00:30:35,510
may not wait until tomorrow.

589
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:37,800
Go get ready.

590
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:38,910
Tonight,

591
00:30:39,110 --> 00:30:40,050
we will steal the bride.

592
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:42,740
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)

593
00:31:02,110 --> 00:31:03,240
I gave you

594
00:31:03,790 --> 00:31:06,030
this whip on your 16th birthday.

595
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:08,270
Are you really throwing it away?

596
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,400
Go away.

597
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,720
Don't bother me again.

598
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,310
Yushan,

599
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:17,720
don't be sad.

600
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:20,960
Even if Mom won't help you,

601
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,400
you still have me.

602
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,550
In the future,

603
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,890
I will help you find a husband

604
00:31:24,910 --> 00:31:26,110
a thousand times better

605
00:31:26,110 --> 00:31:27,350
than Fu Yunxi.

606
00:31:27,960 --> 00:31:30,080
There's nothing in this world
that can't be overcome.

607
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,110
Look at me.

608
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,960
Didn't you say before?

609
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:36,070
Though I can no longer take
the Imperial Exams,

610
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:37,790
there are still many paths ahead.

611
00:31:38,400 --> 00:31:40,550
Why must you fixate on him?

612
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:43,000
I just want to fixate on him.

613
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:43,840
So what?

614
00:31:47,030 --> 00:31:47,870
Zhuang Yuchi,

615
00:31:48,920 --> 00:31:50,720
you are no longer a child.

616
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,270
All this time,

617
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:54,750
Mom and I have been comforting you,

618
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:56,070
but we were just lying.

619
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,030
As a man,

620
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,070
your career is destroyed,

621
00:32:00,960 --> 00:32:03,110
and your life is ruined.

622
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:05,680
You are already a useless man now.

623
00:32:06,240 --> 00:32:07,160
A useless man.

624
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,680
How can a useless man help me?

625
00:32:11,030 --> 00:32:11,870
Yushan...

626
00:32:11,870 --> 00:32:14,200
My life doesn't concern you anymore.

627
00:32:14,590 --> 00:32:15,550
From now on,

628
00:32:15,880 --> 00:32:17,270
none of you should come to see me.

629
00:32:18,550 --> 00:32:19,880
- Leave.
- Yushan.

630
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,080
- Leave!
- Yushan.

631
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:22,110
Leave.

632
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:23,390
Yushan.

633
00:32:24,310 --> 00:32:25,150
Yushan.

634
00:32:34,140 --> 00:32:38,140
(Wedding Procession)

635
00:32:38,140 --> 00:32:39,400
(Fu Mansion)

636
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:40,240
The Fu family?

637
00:32:40,510 --> 00:32:41,650
It's already dark.

638
00:32:41,650 --> 00:32:42,980
Are they going to fetch a bride?

639
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,590
They're probably going
to fetch a second wife.

640
00:32:45,590 --> 00:32:46,750
A second wife?

641
00:32:47,260 --> 00:32:48,740
(Seclusion)

642
00:32:57,030 --> 00:32:58,590
Why haven't they arrived yet?

643
00:33:00,790 --> 00:33:02,790
Master, Master.

644
00:33:03,350 --> 00:33:04,190
How's it going?

645
00:33:04,210 --> 00:33:06,160
Has the matchmaker arrived
with the bridal sedan?

646
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:07,370
I didn't see the matchmaker,

647
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,280
but I saw Mr. Fu,

648
00:33:08,330 --> 00:33:10,670
dressed in wedding attire,
and bringing the bridal sedan.

649
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:12,270
It seems like he's heading to our house.

650
00:33:17,310 --> 00:33:18,720
I've received a secret report.

651
00:33:19,000 --> 00:33:21,680
Villains will take action tonight.

652
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:25,350
Go gather all the officers
at the front gate.

653
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,280
Close the door.

654
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:27,590
- Yes.
- Yes.

655
00:33:27,590 --> 00:33:30,540
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)

656
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:47,000
Miss Hanyan,
your wedding attire is here.

657
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:48,180
Would you like to try it on?

658
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:49,380
If it doesn't fit,

659
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:51,220
I can have them take it back
for alterations.

660
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:52,080
Sure.

661
00:34:24,070 --> 00:34:25,360
It fits perfectly, Miss.

662
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,400
For tomorrow's wedding,

663
00:34:40,280 --> 00:34:41,880
I will wear this goose-shaped hairpin.

664
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:46,760
Miss,

665
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:49,670
won't this hairpin be too informal?

666
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,320
It doesn't matter.

667
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:52,670
Mr. Zhuang has ordered

668
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:53,920
that other than Yuzhu Manor,

669
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:56,030
everyone else should go
to the main door.

670
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:58,340
Let's go.

671
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,200
Yes.

672
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:20,510
Why is the door locked?

673
00:35:22,070 --> 00:35:22,910
Open the door!

674
00:35:23,800 --> 00:35:24,960
Open the door!

675
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:26,480
Open the door!

676
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:35,760
Miss, what's going on?

677
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:39,710
Go find something to step on.

678
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,330
Let's climb over the wall and leave.

679
00:35:41,550 --> 00:35:42,390
Yes.

680
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:47,420
(Wedding Procession, Fu Mansion)

681
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:52,340
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)

682
00:36:06,230 --> 00:36:07,400
We're here to fetch the bride.

683
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,080
Mr. Zhuang, please open the door.

684
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:09,990
It's Mr. Fu.

685
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,480
- Mr. Fu.
- Mr. Fu.

686
00:36:13,550 --> 00:36:15,710
The Emperor has ordered you
to protect me,

687
00:36:16,510 --> 00:36:18,190
so you must follow my orders.

688
00:36:22,660 --> 00:36:24,640
(Zhuang Residence)
We're here to fetch the bride.

689
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,190
Mr. Zhuang, please open the door.

690
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,240
Break down the door.

691
00:36:40,590 --> 00:36:41,800
Go, block the entrance.

692
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:43,440
They must not be allowed in.

693
00:36:45,320 --> 00:36:46,880
If I lose my life,

694
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:48,960
how many lives do you have to spare?

695
00:36:50,510 --> 00:36:51,350
- Yes.
- Yes.

696
00:37:00,660 --> 00:37:02,140
(Seclusion, Zhuang Residence)

697
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,120
Go.

698
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:16,840
Master.

699
00:37:18,110 --> 00:37:19,960
Master, what is happening?

700
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:29,360
Mr. Fu,

701
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:31,670
the Emperor ordered you to protect me.

702
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:34,320
Do you want to defy the Emperor?

703
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,120
Mr. Zhuang,

704
00:37:38,670 --> 00:37:40,360
as per our marriage contract,

705
00:37:40,960 --> 00:37:43,030
I came to take Miss Hanyan as my bride.

706
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,320
You're supposed to stop me
according to customs,

707
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:47,280
but this is too serious for that, right?

708
00:37:48,150 --> 00:37:48,990
Yunxi,

709
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:50,780
you're supposed to get married tomorrow.

710
00:37:51,190 --> 00:37:52,600
What is the meaning of this today?

711
00:37:52,610 --> 00:37:54,800
Are you here to steal the bride?

712
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:57,110
That's right. I've come tonight

713
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,670
to steal the bride.

714
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:03,800
- Young Master Zhuang.
- Young Master Zhuang.

715
00:38:03,800 --> 00:38:04,670
Open the door.

716
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:05,920
Mr. Zhuang has ordered

717
00:38:06,150 --> 00:38:07,590
that no one is allowed in.

718
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,230
The family is in chaos tonight.

719
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:12,280
Father sent me to stay with Hanyan.

720
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:18,230
Go, stop him.

721
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:22,150
We're all colleagues
at the Judicial Review.

722
00:38:22,800 --> 00:38:24,480
We were ordered to protect Mr. Zhuang,

723
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:26,670
but his daughter's marriage

724
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:29,190
is outside our scope of duty.

725
00:38:29,670 --> 00:38:31,000
- Move aside!
- Move aside!

726
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:37,480
Mr. Zhuang, are you

727
00:38:38,510 --> 00:38:41,670
going back on your word again?

728
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:50,680
Zhuang Yuchi,

729
00:38:52,230 --> 00:38:53,150
why are you here?

730
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:56,840
Go and call for help.

731
00:38:57,230 --> 00:38:58,070
Yes.

732
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,150
Zhuang Yuchi,

733
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,770
what exactly do you want to do?

734
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,670
You've ruined my future.

735
00:39:09,190 --> 00:39:10,690
I wasn't going to hold it against you,

736
00:39:11,030 --> 00:39:12,760
but why do you insist

737
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,510
on robbing Yushan of her love?

738
00:39:15,360 --> 00:39:16,670
Rob her of her love?

739
00:39:21,590 --> 00:39:23,800
You've ruined my life anyway.

740
00:39:26,670 --> 00:39:28,510
I have nothing left to lose.

741
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:32,210
Tonight, it should be Yushan
in this wedding attire.

742
00:39:32,630 --> 00:39:33,590
Take it off for her,

743
00:39:34,110 --> 00:39:36,400
so you can fulfill her wish.

744
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:40,470
Take it off!

745
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,320
Don't come closer.

746
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,510
How dare you draw a saber?

747
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:51,320
Zhuang Yuchi, calm down.

748
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:53,190
I never intended to be your enemy.

749
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,670
No more talking! Take it off!

750
00:39:57,760 --> 00:39:58,910
Hand over the wedding attire,

751
00:39:59,550 --> 00:40:00,840
and leave my family.

752
00:40:59,550 --> 00:41:00,390
Yuchi!

753
00:41:01,190 --> 00:41:02,320
- Yuchi!
- Yuchi!

754
00:41:03,630 --> 00:41:04,590
- Yuchi!
- Yuchi!

755
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:05,960
Call the physician!

756
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,480
Go call the physician!

757
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:18,670
- Don't...
- Yushan is right.

758
00:41:20,230 --> 00:41:21,590
I am a useless man.

759
00:41:23,030 --> 00:41:24,230
I've accomplished nothing

760
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:26,710
in my life.

761
00:41:28,140 --> 00:41:29,000
Yuchi...

762
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:30,550
Save your strength. Don't speak.

763
00:41:30,710 --> 00:41:32,190
- Wait for the physician.
- Yuchi...

764
00:42:44,380 --> 00:42:51,380
(Seclusion, Memorial)

765
00:43:08,371 --> 00:43:11,181
♪She hides away her past♪

766
00:43:11,461 --> 00:43:13,791
♪Covered in scars♪

767
