00:44:09,251 --> 00:44:11,711
♪She is willing to become a blade♪

782
00:44:11,711 --> 00:44:13,661
♪Moving forward without retreat♪

783
00:44:13,661 --> 00:44:16,941
♪Charging into this lonely fortress♪

784
00:44:16,941 --> 00:44:19,511
♪Even in a fateful clash♪

785
00:44:19,511 --> 00:44:21,331
♪With eyes stained with blood♪

786
00:44:21,331 --> 00:44:24,581
♪She holds no grudge♪

787
00:44:24,791 --> 00:44:27,151
♪She does not trust fate♪

788
00:44:27,151 --> 00:44:29,191
♪She does not pray to gods♪

789
00:44:29,191 --> 00:44:32,381
♪She grips the blade♪

790
00:44:32,511 --> 00:44:34,981
♪As geese fly south in winter♪

791
00:44:34,981 --> 00:44:36,901
♪She alone journeys north♪

792
00:44:36,901 --> 00:44:43,891
♪Seeking truth in falsehood♪

793
00:44:44,461 --> 00:44:46,741
♪She'd become the blade♪

794
00:44:46,941 --> 00:44:48,711
♪With love as her shield♪

795
00:44:48,711 --> 00:44:52,011
♪Plunging into this mortal world♪

796
00:44:52,211 --> 00:44:54,591
♪Shattering mirages♪

797
00:44:54,591 --> 00:44:56,441
♪And illusions♪

798
00:44:56,441 --> 00:44:59,921
♪To pay respect to the fallen souls♪

799
00:44:59,921 --> 00:45:02,171
♪She does not trust fate♪

800
00:45:02,171 --> 00:45:04,221
♪She does not pray to gods♪

801
00:45:04,221 --> 00:45:07,621
♪She grips the blade♪

802
00:45:07,621 --> 00:45:09,991
♪As geese fly south in winter♪

803
00:45:09,991 --> 00:45:12,091
♪She alone journeys north♪

804
00:45:12,091 --> 00:45:17,971
♪Seeking only a trace♪

805
00:45:19,051 --> 00:45:22,531
♪Of warmth♪

